.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-7::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, gardening, traveling, writing
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, dancer, doctor, videographer
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, fish, goldfish, hedgehog
 1. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
 2. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is traveling##3
 3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3
 4. the doctor is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
 5. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 6. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 7. the doctor is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 8. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the videographer##3
 9. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
10. the dancer is on the left or right of the doctor##3
11. the dancer is the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Hobby         | traveling    | camping  | gardening | writing   |
| Job           | videographer | dancer   | doctor    | bartender |
| Pet   | hedgehog      | goldfish | fish | chinchilla  |

