3. the indonesian is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3
4. the owner of the turtle is between the person eating eggplant and the polish##2
5. the person eating eggplant is the argentine##1
6. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the argentine##3
7. the owner of the rat is on the far left##1
8. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the person eating lemon##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |      3       |     4      |
| Food           | garlic | lemon | grapefruit | eggplant      |
| Nationality   | indonesian   | polish | french       | argentine  |
| Pet           | rat          | snake  | turtle       | guinea-pig |

