5. the american is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left##1
7. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the australian##3
8. the spanish is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |      3      |      4      |
