4. the argentine is on the far left or far right##3
5. the indian is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
6. the person eating mango is on the left of the argentine##1
7. the fan of r&b is the malaysian##1
8. the person eating asparagus is between the fan of r&b and the fan of metal##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |     4     |
